text: Lillan Elisabeth Westli (born 15 February 1972) is a Norwegian speed skater. She represented Norway and Kongsvinger Idrettslag. She won the 1989 Norwegian Championships, in relay. She competed at the 2000/2001 ISU Speed Skating World Cup, and 2001/2002 ISU Speed Skating World Cup. == References == Category:1972 births Category:Norwegian speed skaters Category:Living people
